It may also belong to "Sound" (cs.SD) as it deals with acoustic modeling and signal processing. Additionally, it may be relevant to "Machine Learning" (cs.LG) as it involves training a neural network model, and "Systems and Control" (cs.SY) as it deals with improving the performance of an ASR system in uncontrolled environments.
